| **Operation**    | **Data Structure Used** | **Reason for Choosing the DS**                                     |
| ---------------- | ----------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Push Item        | Stack                   | LIFO method fast add operations ke liye best hai (Undo/History).   |
| Pop Item         | Stack                   | Last added element ko remove karna bohot easy hota hai.            |
| Peek Top Element | Stack                   | Last item check karna without removing possible hota hai.          |

